---
title: Greek-Style Lemon-Pepper Meatballs with Buttery Orzo
description: Opa! Tonight we present Greek-spiced pork meatballs and buttery lemon orzo pasta, studded with olives and roasted peppers! A dollop of tzatziki crowns this bowl of Grecian wonders!
